data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 11/25/2023 11AM-2PM ** Stunning 4bedroom 2.5 bathroom second story home in Parkwood has gorgeous upgrades throughout and is priced to sell.  This home features the following: two car garage, mostly laminate flooring, open floor plan in the kitchen and living room area, iron stairway rails, ceiling fans in all bedrooms, kitchen has all the bells and whistles you've been looking for with large beautiful portable island that conveys, dining room area is separate, all bedrooms upstairs, new interior paint, plenty of natural light throughout, primary bedroom is generous in space and has his and hers walk-in closets, double vanities, upgraded light fixtures, combo shower/tub in both full bathrooms, other bedrooms are perfect in size, the backyard has covered patio great for entertainment and storage shed conveys as well. This home is close to shopping centers, restaurants and great schools.
